The first scan shows strong adjusted main effects and one dominant interaction pattern: palbociclib benefit concentrates in ER/PR-positive, lower Ki-67, PIK3CA-wild-type profiles and is attenuated in HER2-positive or triple-negative disease. I’m running a second pass over non-treatment clinical interactions so the transcript covers prognostic heterogeneity, not only treatment effects.
