summary.push('Finally, receptor and mutation interaction tests refined the biomarker story. '+[line('h25b','PIK3CA mutation by ER-positive interaction'),line('h25c','Above-median Ki-67 by ER-positive interaction')].join(' ')+' These results indicate that PIK3CA mutation and high proliferation were especially adverse in ER-positive tumors.');
